{"tid":225850,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ 巴塞下季波衫最終版曝光！新贊助商登場","createTime":"2017-05-02T05:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T11:20:24.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8977bb2e9c5d9682800b6dc11581c025352731","tid":225850,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"在多次遭到提前曝光之後，巴塞下季波衫的最終版本終於出爐了。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據足球裝備領域專業網站「footyheadlines」曝光的諜照，巴塞新賽季波衫的最終版本終於面世。<br />\n<br />\n　　在此之前，巴塞新賽季波衫也曾不只一次被曝光，不過，在這些曝光的版本中，波衫胸前並沒有巴塞新贊助商日本樂天的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n　　在本次的曝光版本中，波衫胸前終於有了贊助商的標誌。日本樂天集團的商標位於波衫正面中間位置，顏色為白色。整件波衫依然延續了巴塞傳統的紅藍色。藍色的背景下，波衫正面為紅色的豎條紋，這些條紋從中間向兩邊逐漸變窄。<br />\n<br />\n　　在日本樂天標誌的上方，左側為波衫贊助商NIKE的標誌，右邊則是巴塞的球隊隊徽。衣領為圓領設計，周圍為黃色條紋的點綴。<br />\n<br />\n　　波衫背部，依然是和正面相同的豎條紋設計，波衫正下方為聯合國兒童基金會的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/05/02/4/446ec581851328d833cab5291d8b09a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F05%2F02%2F4%2F446ec581851328d833cab5291d8b09a0.jpg&h=2442a79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/05/02/1/1cb1825a149585df6e0ea861c090063e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F05%2F02%2F1%2F1cb1825a149585df6e0ea861c090063e.jpg&h=83114234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a187b267fd70f85c6a211b98383ccf5e0c59bb04","tid":225850,"uid":102643,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20041129/Article_LiveMag/29fo2pPath.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20041129%2FArticle_LiveMag%2F29fo2pPath.jpg&h=52cc1a28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54f6775cf0e7c346db741bc449977347eefe37f9","tid":225850,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"<bloc